          <mj-text color="#24226A" font-weight="bold" font-size="18px" line-height="22px" padding-bottom="8px">Non-NCPD Innovation Showcase: Deplete to Defeat: Asparagine Depletion in T-Cell ALL</mj-text>
          <mj-text color="#142D51" font-size="16px">Presented by Katherine Mason, MSN, APRN, PNP-PC, CPHON</mj-text>
          <mj-social font-size="14px" icon-size="30px" mode="horizontal" align="left" padding="0" text-padding="0 5px">
