          </mj-social>
          <mj-text padding-top="15px" font-size="14px" padding-right="10px">This presentation will provide an overview of the role of asparagine depletion in T-cell ALL and the use of asparaginase in the treatment of pediatric, adolescent, and young adult patients.</mj-text>
          <mj-button href="https://aphon2023.eventscribe.net/index.asp?presTarget=2522305" background-color="#D44233" color="white" align="left" padding-left="0" width="169px" font-weight="bold">Learn more</mj-button>
